OL,5,G0105 GPs Behind Closed Doors
OL,6,     FThe doctors of Hall Green Health
OL,7,     Fcome face to face with some rare
OL,8,     Fconditions. It's a reminder that
OL,9,     Fwhen you're a GP, you never know
OL,10,     Fwhat is going to walk through your
OL,11,     Fdoor.
OL,12,G0200 Casualty 24/7: Every Second Counts
OL,13,     FA two-year-old girl is brought in
OL,14,     Fwhile she deals with dangerously
OL,15,     Flow blood sugar levels; junior
OL,16,     Fdoctor Alex Chatburn has his own
OL,17,     Fviews on emergency admissions.
OL,18,G0250 Skin A&E
OL,19,     FA look at misbehaving lumps, from
OL,20,     Fthe biggest (13cm) to the smallest
OL,21,     Fthat the dermatologists have ever
OL,22,     Ftreated.
